title: Aaron Rodgers, OBJ, Sam Darnold, and starting QBs
itunes:title: Aaron Rodgers, OBJ, Sam Darnold, and starting QBs
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb talks about Green Bay Packers QB Aaron Rodgers' new contract, the New York Giants giving WR Odell Beckham Jr. what he wants, the New York Jets starting QB Sam Darnold, and the 10 worst starting QBs in the NFL. Guests include Mark Schlereth, Rob Ryan, and Tyron Woodley.
